            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-4">Sweet and vibrant purple yam (Ube) cream with a rich center. A local favorite.</p>
            <button class="w-full bg-pink-500 text-white font-medium py-2 px-4 rounded-full hover:bg-pink-600 transition duration-300 text-sm">
                Order This Flavor
            </button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="flavor-card bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl overflow-hidden">
        <img src="mango.jpg"
            alt="Mango Burst Puffstilla"
            onerror="this.onerror=null; this.src='https://placehold.co/400x300/fbcfe8/be185d?text=Image+Missing'"
            class="w-full h-48 object-cover object-center">
        <div class="p-4 text-center">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-extrabold text-pink-700 mb-2">Mango Burst</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-4">Tropical mango jam filling for a bright and tangy experience. Perfect for summer.</p>
            <button class="w-full bg-pink-500 text-white font-medium py-2 px-4 rounded-full hover:bg-pink-600 transition duration-300 text-sm">
                Order This Flavor
            </button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="flavor-card bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl overflow-hidden">
        <img src="matcha.jpg"
            alt="Matcha Dream Puffstilla"
            onerror="this.onerror=null; this.src='https://placehold.co/400x300/fbcfe8/be185d?text=Image+Missing'"
            class="w-full h-48 object-cover object-center">
        <div class="p-4 text-center">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-extrabold text-pink-700 mb-2">Matcha Dream</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-4">Earthy matcha sponge and cream with a delicate green tea filling. Subtle and sophisticated.</p>
            <button class="w-full bg-pink-500 text-white font-medium py-2 px-4 rounded-full hover:bg-pink-600 transition duration-300 text-sm">
                Order This Flavor
            </button>
        </div>
    </div>

</div>

<div class="mt-12 text-center p-6 bg-pink-100 rounded-xl border border-pink-300">
<p class="text-xl font-extrabold text-pink-700">Can't choose? Try one of each! It's always DESSERT TIME.</p>
</div>
</div>
</section>

</main>

<footer class="bg-gray-900 text-white p-4 mt-auto w-full">
<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto text-center text-sm flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-between items-center">
<p class="text-gray-400">&copy; 2025 Puffstillas. All rights reserved.</p>
<p class="mt-2 sm:mt-0">
Email: <a href="mailto:puffstillas.sweets@gmail.com" class="text-pink-400 hover:text-pink-300 transition duration-150 font-medium">puffstillas.sweets@gmail.com</a>
</p>
</div>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
